::Rex::

Rex frowns, looking at Battera. "Allright, so let me get this straight," he 
says, grabbing yet another fruit, "A 'very special' Pred is hosting a peace 
meeting. I assume his crew also consists of Predacons. The Predacon, 
Alliance, and Maximal commanders are to be present there."

His eyes narrow as his mind jumps to the worst conclusion. "Sounds like an 
ambush to me."
